description: The Invesco China Technology ETF (Fund) is based on the FTSE China Incl A 25% Technology Capped Index (Index). The Fund will invest at least 90% of its total assets in securities that comprise the Index as well as American depositary receipts and global depositary receipts based on the securities in the Index. The Index includes constituents of the FTSE China Index and FTSE China A Stock Connect Index that are classified as information technology securities, including China A-shares and China B-shares. The Fund and the Index are rebalanced quarterly.Effective at market open on January 5, 2024, Invesco's management fees for Invesco China Technology ETF (Ticker: CQQQ) will be reduced from 70 basis points to 65 basis points.
name: Invesco China Technology ETF
